<GUIClass name="CMUI_HazardsListTable" id="4847d9e4-8de1-4fa1-a73a-908d8aa2aa80">
    <superclass name="Table"/>
    <transient/>
    <sharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassSharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>
Custom control which has a column which is a listbox.  A collection
can be attached to the control and it will maintain a list of all the
objects checked (self.allSelectedObjects).

Copied to accommodate additional hazard information (UNDG numbers).
Has an extra column added for this additional info.</text>
    <DbClassMap file="_usergui"/>
